    <title>Python z3用法</title>
    <link href="http://yjw1029.github.io/tools/Python%20z3%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95.html"/>
    <id>http://yjw1029.github.io/tools/Python z3用法.html</id>
    <published>2019-04-08T12:20:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-04-10T06:04:33.203Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a><h2 id="Install-安装方法"><a href="#Install-安装方法" class="headerlink" title="Install 安装方法"></a>Install 安装方法</h2><p>直接下载<a href="https://github.com/angr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">angr</a>,一个非常好用的符号分析工具之后也会用到</p><h2 id="入门学习"><a href="#入门学习" class="headerlink" title="入门学习"></a>入门学习</h2><h3 id="基本操作"><a href="#基本操作" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h3><ol><li><p>定义整形变量：<code>x = Int(&#39;x&#39;)</code>, <code>y = Int(&#39;y&#39;)</code></p></li><li><p>解不等式：<code>solve(约束条件1，约束条件2，··· 约束条件n)</code> 使用运算符&lt;, &lt;=, &gt;, &gt;=, ==, != 来进行比较</p></li><li><p>使用simplify()进行表达式化简:</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x + y + <span class="number">2</span>*x +<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x &lt; y + x + <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(And(x+<span class="number">1</span>&gt;=<span class="number">3</span>, x**<span class="number">2</span> + x**<span class="number">2</span> + y**<span class="number">2</span> + <span class="number">2</span> &gt;= <span class="number">5</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span> + <span class="number">3</span>*x + y</span><br><span class="line">Not(y &lt;= <span class="number">-2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">And(x &gt;= <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>*x**<span class="number">2</span> + y**<span class="number">2</span> &gt;= <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li><p><code>set_option(html_mode = True)</code>使得Z3Py以Z3Py表示法显示</p></li><li><p>Z3 提供遍历表达式的函数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">n = x + y &gt;= <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"num args: "</span>, n.num_args()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"children: "</span>, n.children()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"1st child: "</span>, n.arg(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"2nd child: "</span>, n.arg(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"operator: "</span>, n.decl()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"op name: "</span>, n.decl().name()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">num args: <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">children: [x+y, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>st child: x+y</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>nd child: <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">operator: &gt;=</span><br><span class="line">op name: &gt;=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>Real(&#39;x&#39;) Reals(&#39;x y z&#39;)</code>创建实数变量。z3py可以表示任意大的整数，有理数和无理数。使用<code>set_option(preciosion=num)</code>可以将结果显示精确到指定的位数。输出时<code>?</code>表示输出被截断。</p><p>注： set_option()用于配置z3全局环境</p></li><li><p>注意z3py中 <code>1/3</code>是python表达式而不是有理数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 有理数的正确表示方法 1/3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> Q(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> RealVal(<span class="number">1</span>)/<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + Q(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + <span class="string">"1/3"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + <span class="number">0.25</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>set_option(rational_to_decimal=True)</code>可以强制将有理数输出为十进制小数</p></li><li><p>若约束条件不可满足，系统会输出<code>no solution</code></p></li></ol><h3 id="布尔逻辑"><a href="#布尔逻辑" class="headerlink" title="布尔逻辑"></a>布尔逻辑</h3><p>Z3支持Bool运算符： And, Or, Not, Implies(implication), If(if-then-else)和==运算符</p><ol><li>定义布尔变量 <code>Bool(&#39;p&#39;)</code> `x, y ,z = Bools(‘x y z’)</li><li>Implies(p, q)表示p蕴含q</li><li>使用solve添加布尔运算约束条件，当三个布尔表达式皆为真时求得解。</li><li>基本布尔运算符And()与, Or()或，Not()非，Nand()与非，Nor()或非，Xor()异或，Implies()蕴含，Equivalent()双蕴含，If(t1, t2, t3)若t1为真t2否则为t3</li><li>True Flase 作为bool常量</li></ol><h3 id="求解器"><a href="#求解器" class="headerlink" title="求解器"></a>求解器</h3><ol><li><p>基本用法</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义求解器</span></span><br><span class="line">s = Solver() <span class="comment">#求解器初始时为空</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line">s.add(x&gt;<span class="number">10</span>, y==x+<span class="number">2</span>) </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 判断是否有解，有解返回sat 无解返回unsat</span></span><br><span class="line">s.check()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保存当前的约束条件至一个栈中</span></span><br><span class="line">s.push()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 从栈中取出最近一次保存的约束条件作为当前的约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line">s.pop()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>z3可以解决线性多项式，非线性多项式的问题z3将无法解决返回unknown</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Real(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(<span class="number">2</span>**x == <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unknown</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>遍历/性能统计</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x,y = Reals(<span class="string">'x y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(x&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, y&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, Or(x+y&gt;<span class="number">3</span>, x-y&lt;<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打印约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> c <span class="keyword">in</span> s.assertations():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> c</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查是否有满足约束条件的解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 性能统计</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.statistics()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> k,v <span class="keyword">in</span> s.statistics():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"%s, %s"</span> % (k,v)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>检查模型，用于输出Solver()的解</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输入约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line">x, y, z = Reals(<span class="string">'x y z'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(x&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, y&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, x+y&gt;<span class="number">3.</span> z-x&lt;<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 开始使用模型求解了，只会输出第一个解</span></span><br><span class="line">m = s.model()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出x变量的解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"x =%s"</span> % m[x]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出所有的解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> d <span class="keyword">in</span> m.decls():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">'%s = %s'</span> % (d.name(), m[d])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="ARITHMETIC-算数"><a href="#ARITHMETIC-算数" class="headerlink" title="ARITHMETIC 算数"></a>ARITHMETIC 算数</h3>]]></content>
    
